{"tid":426958,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想當年我同學唔讀civil轉系讀Physics","createTime":"2017-10-07T05:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T09:47:22.000Z","uid":103237,"like":34,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f0db176f73cdf92e9f074ae9771c30951df30b","tid":426958,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:59:46.000Z","msg":"今天,他已經成為一個老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日上幾堂照書讀,玩下細路,三點幾又收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦有條穩定career path<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然係毒撚底亦有不少女仕垂青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而civil,已經再踏入冰河時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有牌工程師都失業要去M記坐扮番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n更遑論要成家立室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗番自己讀咁耐書,結果落得如此下場,真係愧對納稅人...哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed246cb89554656cf4afdf684a1d186adabc936","tid":426958,"uid":103237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"呢篇Discuss野我十年前已經睇到<br />\n但當年都唔識驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&quot;如果十年後Civil Eng市況又變爛了<br />\n<br />\n到時候已有三十幾四十歲了吧?<br />\n<br />\n人到中年, 而且多數一家幾口吧? 手停也差不多要口停了.<br />\n再等 Civil Eng 下一個小陽春, 還是轉行<br />\n<br />\n總會有行業不介意中年人士轉行的,<br />\n但大多是服務業, 或大部份收入靠銷售,<br />\n或者要到僱員再培訓局參加再培訓課程嗎?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n呢家,真係驚都太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3c427062843e6e06d256fd7ca9e44658f22f43","tid":426958,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:09:25.000Z","msg":"呢篇都係<br />\n十年前既文<br />\n而家竟然同我情況差唔多,我爭在冇去搵Professor訴苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&quot;真實個案.....<br />\n<br />\n我當日死死地氣....去搵個 Professor 幫我寫 reference letter 去報讀 Master 既時候，當我準備入佢間房之際....我竟然....聽到有哭聲...係一個男人既哭聲....<br />\n<br />\n我在出面偷聽到少少.....跟住個男人出黎...我入去 Professor 間房....言談之後，先知道...果個男人係大我兩年既師兄....剛剛考了 Engine 牌...在一間跨國既顧問公司工作了四年....由於工程不景氣，佢考左 Engine 牌竟然冇位上，局住做番 Assistant Engineer...人工冇得升.....<br />\n<br />\n個 professor 仲講呢個師兄當年以十分優異既成績考入尼個 Engine 課程(唔知個 professor 有冇吹水喇...佢話尼個師兄當年Jupas 剩係揀左三個 choices 係 band A..1. HKU Civil Engineering, 2. MBBS, 3. HKU AC 其他 choices 全部冇填).....亦都以 First Hon 畢業....但最後出黎既....竟然係四年後冇位上、冇得加人工........<br />\n<br />\n而且佢同屆既中學同學...大部份都學有所成 (非 Engine 既同學 )...人工高過佢一截.....真係慘.......估唔到&quot;一子錯&quot;...真係會搞到&quot;滿盆皆落索&quot;.......個師兄果陣時應該 27-28 歲喇....想轉行都唔得喇....<br />\n<br />\n所以千祈唔好揀 CIVIL ENGINEERING 呀！&quot;"},{"pid":"4c0d2ffb6255b363b34ac7cc2e380dbc6f3d95d8","tid":426958,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:12:11.000Z","msg":"為咗唔令civil爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bc1701f45e181a87ce675e4ed13f0839267387","tid":426958,"uid":103237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:12:38.000Z","msg":"呢篇都係好中<br />\n其實係當你對得多engine野<br />\n思維上自然只係識抄野<br />\n咩soft skill, creativity已經無哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&quot;問咁多位engin同學<br />\n有冇試過搵工時因為自己個degree有engineering依個字, 而俾人歧視/ 第一印覺得你唔適合呢??<br />\n舉個例子, management trainee require 既係communication skill, problem solving skill, 但當engin人interview既時候, 佢又會問: 你係一個engin人, 點解會 apply management既工..................咁即係佢心目中覺得, engin 人係唔會適合做management既野........(當然歧視程度未必高, 但一定有)....<br />\n<br />\n舉多一個例子, 今年johnson &amp; johnson 係科大請人, 佢話咩degree都歡迎, 但shortlist後就全部都係bba人........係唔係真係無任何一個engin人match到佢要求??定佢地本身就歧視左engin人呢??&quot;"},{"pid":"b160cf71257b344657f7219bca6b0f709b558aa7","tid":426958,"uid":22808,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:14:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>廢就廢啦，唔係覺得你讀Phy就搵到食？</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"08214e7125939249437cae63cd73cfffd19bee6d","tid":426958,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:38:35.000Z","msg":"Z大潮文update版<br />\n但大致上都係中<br />\n<br />\n最重要係呢篇文係十年前已經係Discuss出現<br />\n當年果位人兄真係睇得好透<br />\n<br />\n粗略更正番D Project完工期<br />\n<br />\n&quot;如果你細心留意下近期推出的大型基建，都趕係 2016-2017 年完成。<br />\n<br />\n同埋機場加西九都係大約1600至1700億，但係 2017 年前會有約 2400-2500 億工程完工.<br />\n有一部份從業員可能會被淘汰或減人工.<br />\n<br />\n1. 郵輪碼頭 (2013 年中完工)<br />\n2. 西港島線 (2015 年頭完工)<br />\n3. 南港島線 (2016 年尾完工)<br />\n4. 高鐵線 (預計 2018 尾完工)<br />\n5. 港珠澳橋 (預計 2017 年尾完工)<br />\n6. 中環繞道 (預計 2018 年完工)<br />\n7. 吐露港/粉嶺道路工程 (預計 2019 年完工)<br />\n8. 屯門西繞道工程 (無限延期,或最終不會上馬)<br />\n<br />\n加埋差唔多成二千幾億工程..2017 年左右前完工 ，另外機場第三條跑道未必會如期 2015 年動工，因為受環評限制......，到時分分鐘有裁員潮. (特別是新入行、年資較少的畢業生....因為公司會減少資源去培訓新血，新血未夠能力去 RUN JOB.....)<br />\n依家先入行真係要諗清楚。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 2003 年一個 fresh chartered engineer/QS 人工為 $13-15K.&quot;"},{"pid":"f0bc21b1b4a45eeb7fb5311bfd279df77c5b9f1a","tid":426958,"uid":116213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你讀civil都可以去教physics"},{"pid":"95a59dad7dc70a8b0dab5603504daf23851c2758","tid":426958,"uid":87339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你讀civil都可以去教physics</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n十年前就係<br />\n<br />\n校長問你 你唔係讀physics憑乜教physics就即刻收皮"},{"pid":"98175016c0e7e216b00a4a8090e2a0a920468f91","tid":426958,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T06:54:45.000Z","msg":"physics都有人吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722986a6518a4670436d8f9b14c0f27ca3aa5784","tid":426958,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T08:44:21.000Z","msg":"樓主似吹淡civil多喎<br />\n<br />\n用physics做比較啫"},{"pid":"6ce4fb5a92e5bd52cdb4c9aa62b3e450478e0ba0","tid":426958,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a768a667152120e8783db54ce2de076c2d54d6df","tid":426958,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:44:24.000Z","msg":"而家讀physics 教育界都食唔到咁多畢業生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1dbbd4f525453873bbb4b140fab124994dcd617","tid":426958,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:51:43.000Z","msg":"讀完civil 出黎做野真係辛苦到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581cfff464d24048376c64f89f8a1e915b262d5c","tid":426958,"uid":133480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有啟德 新東北"},{"pid":"723c5e2994b7e3599c773080b6e299f3f6a62340","tid":426958,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:39:56.000Z","msg":"依家仲讀緊書既朋友真係恭喜哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f96dad44680d3ed35d533d1199b71b59e33ba3e","tid":426958,"uid":152090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0b302437afabb00bb9123802e1b3e6f79cf5d6","tid":426958,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:32:06.000Z","ms